Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.40,0:01:41.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在正義中迷失的那段日子裏
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.33,0:01:47.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我無論在哪裡..無論和誰..
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.68,0:02:06.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小葉！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.85,0:02:10.25,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(550,0)}派對
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.86,0:02:29.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為下週有游泳的考試
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.93,0:02:34.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以如果不練的更熟練一點會出洋相的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.85,0:02:36.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.78,0:02:44.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我走了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.61,0:02:48.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小葉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.51,0:02:51.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.46,0:02:56.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥的正義是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.54,0:03:02.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我看來你只是想得到別人的夸耀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.73,0:03:11.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定會變強的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.39,0:03:16.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想讓妳也明白我的正義
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.34,0:03:22.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.23,0:03:28.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個笑容猶如拒人於千里之外
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.47,0:03:31.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是..
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.39,0:03:35.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在的我可不同哦 小葉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.37,0:03:49.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽如果回來的話 請轉達她不要擔心我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.31,0:03:50.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.16,0:03:53.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不認為這是陷阱嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.17,0:03:58.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是之前以試煉之名義而試探你的男人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.30,0:04:01.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要小葉有在他手上的可能性
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.95,0:04:02.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就非去不可
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.12,0:04:22.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很幸福哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.99,0:04:24.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.37,0:04:27.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在非常地..幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.29,0:04:36.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想要買房子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.56,0:04:38.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒..房子？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.78,0:04:42.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,賺錢買房子 和家人生活在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.25,0:04:44.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是我的夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.69,0:04:48.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我第一次救妳的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.89,0:04:50.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,問妳要過謝禮一萬元吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.29,0:04:51.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.67,0:04:55.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難不成你想以那種方式賺錢嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.27,0:04:57.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是我的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.48,0:05:00.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,工作之後收取報酬是理所當然的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.52,0:05:03.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可我沒有付哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.81,0:05:04.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會收妳的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.73,0:05:06.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.75,0:05:10.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我想和妳成為家人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.35,0:05:20.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要接啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.57,0:05:23.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可不行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.16,0:05:29.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高雅 怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.52,0:05:31.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小葉她？！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.58,0:05:45.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你來得正好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.98,0:05:49.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請上車吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.34,0:05:51.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來帶路
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.92,0:05:53.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小葉在那裡嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.25,0:05:59.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始移動了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.54,0:06:01.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始追蹤！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.14,0:06:16.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是所謂的正義試煉嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.76,0:06:19.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這麼認為嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.79,0:06:20.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的目的是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.82,0:06:23.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到時候你就會明白的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.49,0:06:28.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關於小葉你還沒回答我呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.32,0:06:41.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.09,0:06:45.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,系統沒有反應啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.16,0:06:46.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.18,0:06:47.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早見先生！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.92,0:06:51.72,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追蹤信號01 信號級別
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.28,0:06:50.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我這裡也接收不到高雅的信號
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.02,0:06:53.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是發生了什麼事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.68,0:06:54.53,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信號級別
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.12,0:06:55.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之要把那輛車找出來！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.68,0:06:57.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.03,0:06:59.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我這邊也盡快想辦法修復
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.78,0:07:06.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要走了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.25,0:07:08.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事情不妙了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.93,0:07:15.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等我回來了 我會把一切都告訴妳
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.57,0:07:17.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切是指？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.55,0:07:22.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關於我的事情 我唯獨想讓妳知道這一切
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.02,0:07:28.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳會等我嗎？在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.14,0:07:30.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.58,0:07:33.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我等著
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.86,0:07:39.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 會長
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.73,0:07:43.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身邊有親密的人感覺還真是不錯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.19,0:07:50.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你醒了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.59,0:07:58.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那支耳機請務必不要摘下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.71,0:08:02.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為那可是和我取得聯系的唯一手段
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.46,0:08:09.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 測試開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.49,0:08:13.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請不用擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.18,0:08:16.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的武裝我完全沒動
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.73,0:08:18.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們都想來一場公平勝負吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.93,0:08:24.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切斷和外界的聯絡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.61,0:08:25.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還敢說這樣公平？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.08,0:08:28.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,測試要憑你一人之力
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.31,0:08:30.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是來見小葉的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.73,0:08:33.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是來參加測試的！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.19,0:08:37.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很遺憾 你妹妹不在這裡哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.93,0:08:40.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,測試從那通電話就開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.90,0:08:45.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綁架你真是容易呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.19,0:08:47.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開什麼玩笑！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.53,0:08:50.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果小葉不在的話我要回去了！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.98,0:08:53.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你覺得真的不在這嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.68,0:08:57.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不覺得剛才我的話也是騙人的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.03,0:09:02.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來到我跟前你就會知道真相了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.56,0:09:04.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來找我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.08,0:09:06.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會在一旁看著你的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.21,0:09:44.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.21,0:09:46.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個很好吃呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.55,0:09:50.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.97,0:09:53.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的好好吃哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.19,0:09:57.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好吃吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.10,0:10:03.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高雅同學！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.82,0:10:09.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.27,0:10:11.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是派對啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.48,0:10:13.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自從那次放火事件以來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.26,0:10:17.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就成為了女孩子們心目中的偶像了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.02,0:10:21.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也是測試
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.24,0:10:25.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要以尋找我確認妹妹安危為優先
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.29,0:10:28.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是要帶著她們逃走
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.87,0:10:35.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前我記得好像選擇了妹妹 讓三個無辜的人死去了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.39,0:10:39.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家 請等一下！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.70,0:10:48.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 給簽個名吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.34,0:10:49.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.30,0:10:52.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我倒不是你的粉絲
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.95,0:10:54.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是有熟人拜託我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.35,0:10:57.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿到簽名我馬上就離開了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.10,0:10:59.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點簽一個吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.64,0:11:02.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.67,0:11:06.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先讓我去一次洗手間 可以嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.26,0:11:07.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.78,0:11:08.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.14,0:11:10.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洗手間在那邊哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.62,0:11:11.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.70,0:11:14.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶 去偷看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.50,0:11:15.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不如乾脆推了他？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.33,0:11:29.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,選擇去找他 結果最後還是沒弄清楚小葉的下落的話..
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.00,0:11:32.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他已經殺了三個人了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.51,0:11:34.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他自己承認了！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.49,0:11:39.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦 我不能放任她們不管
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.98,0:11:46.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小葉 妳真的在這裡嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.90,0:11:53.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難不成..
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.96,0:12:01.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.40,0:12:03.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿姨 是我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.82,0:12:05.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿人..？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.89,0:12:13.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起逃吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.53,0:12:15.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.08,0:12:18.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不覺得這裡很奇怪嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.15,0:12:22.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手機沒有信號 你覺得這可能嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.87,0:12:28.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我去找了找到外面去的出口
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.71,0:12:29.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.33,0:12:32.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這女孩怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.60,0:12:35.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也是那傢伙的測試嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.85,0:12:40.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請看這裡 你瞧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.72,0:12:51.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧 很奇怪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.96,0:12:56.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.98,0:12:58.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.52,0:13:00.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高雅同學 我們走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.08,0:13:03.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡絕對很奇怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.44,0:13:06.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下 那邊的情況..
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.44,0:13:09.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 你在這裡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.93,0:13:12.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過來嘛 高雅同學
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.65,0:13:15.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出現了一個新的房間呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.69,0:13:16.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新的房間？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.28,0:13:18.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 要不要來看看？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.54,0:13:21.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 過一會我就去..
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.09,0:13:23.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 快點來哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.82,0:13:24.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都等著你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.48,0:13:28.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶 高雅同學..
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.23,0:13:31.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那邊發生了什麼狀況
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.81,0:13:33.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不定是新的陷阱
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.84,0:13:37.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不..這個逃生通道才是陷阱麼..
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.26,0:13:41.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是說這個是接近他的通道嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.21,0:13:44.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該確認一下那邊出現的房間
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.40,0:13:47.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要用這個逃生通道的話 就大家一起用
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.73,0:13:50.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 大家一起的話..
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.58,0:13:56.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿人的話 就會救所有人！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.27,0:13:59.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳先走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.63,0:14:01.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果這條路通到外面的話
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.34,0:14:03.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趕緊去報警
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.39,0:14:05.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高雅同學呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.98,0:14:07.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要救所有人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.98,0:14:11.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正如妳所說 這裡是非常危險的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.74,0:14:13.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.66,0:14:14.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳快點走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.95,0:14:22.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶 看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.84,0:14:24.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看 就是那個房間哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.23,0:14:28.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位 高雅同學回來了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.75,0:14:31.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高雅同學
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.45,0:14:37.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她在幹什麼呀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.52,0:14:45.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高雅同學..
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.09,0:14:50.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你又選錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.23,0:14:51.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.54,0:15:10.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.48,0:15:11.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打不開！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.85,0:15:12.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,究竟怎麼回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.98,0:15:13.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開門啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.93,0:15:14.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰來開個門啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.55,0:15:17.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位 冷靜一下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.77,0:15:20.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這個殺人犯！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.40,0:15:22.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.50,0:15:24.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽我說
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.57,0:15:25.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不要你的藉口
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.19,0:15:28.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點把我們從這裡放出去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.02,0:15:32.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開了..
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.62,0:15:37.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下 那邊危險！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.64,0:15:39.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請等一下！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.25,0:15:43.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太過分了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.09,0:15:46.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都不聽別人解釋就出手打人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.07,0:15:51.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位 請等一下！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.16,0:16:00.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騙人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.09,0:16:14.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞什麼啊 為什麼又打不開了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.23,0:16:15.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給你一個新的測試吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.99,0:16:22.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有沒有聽到什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.42,0:16:42.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請認真聽我說
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.33,0:16:48.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,道路盡頭有來到我這的電梯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.00,0:16:52.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要丟下她們跑到這裡來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.31,0:16:55.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是要打倒巨錘兵 然後和大家一起來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.94,0:16:58.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正義在哪一方？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.77,0:16:59.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那還用說
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.58,0:17:03.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刀模式
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.57,0:17:09.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不打倒邪惡如何稱為正義！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.05,0:17:14.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真可悲呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.13,0:17:23.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,氣氛越來越熱烈了呢 次郎先生
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.73,0:17:26.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 我也差不多該..
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.77,0:17:32.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以嗎 不讓他知道妳在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.80,0:17:35.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我現在不想和任何人說話
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.13,0:17:38.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我又是什麼呀
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.51,0:17:40.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明美阿姨是例外
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.27,0:17:44.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種時候妳倒是不去依靠阿人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.66,0:17:49.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是現在 阿人也讓我覺得害怕..
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.51,0:17:58.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明發生著什麼 可是沒有人肯告訴我真相
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.81,0:18:03.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼要緊的時候 妳居然會想起我讓我很欣慰呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.74,0:18:05.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿人走了之後
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.36,0:18:09.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我感覺心裏出現了一個大洞呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.77,0:18:14.65,Zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}阿姨 妳過得還好吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.77,0:18:14.65,Zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}請原諒我的不辭而別。發生了不少事情
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.77,0:18:14.65,Zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}讓我也有些不知所措，所以這麼晚才來跟您報告
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.77,0:18:14.65,Zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}我現在過得還蠻不錯的，雖然父母突然出現在面前
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.77,0:18:14.65,Zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}也沒法一下子就適應。不過我過得還好。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.77,0:18:14.65,Zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}阿姨妳倒是，好像自己的親身兒子要回來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.77,0:18:14.65,Zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}父母也說會盡力幫助妳。這樣阿姨也不會覺得
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.77,0:18:14.65,Zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}孤獨了呢！太棒了！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.77,0:18:14.65,Zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}然後呢，妳有空的時候去看一看，不是有一張為了我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.77,0:18:14.65,Zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}而買的書桌嗎。雖然到最後，我還是從來沒用到過。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.77,0:18:14.65,Zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}去檢查一下那個書桌的桌背。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.77,0:18:14.65,Zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}那份禮物我遲早會送給阿姨的 所以請收下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.77,0:18:14.65,Zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}為防止妳亂猜亂想所以我先解釋一下 這是我打工賺來的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.77,0:18:14.65,Zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}絕不是偷來搶來的。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.70,0:18:13.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那封信 妳讀了好多次呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.64,0:18:19.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿人他..真的去了親生父母身邊了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.66,0:18:20.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.88,0:18:23.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為..他一直都待在下城
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.14,0:18:29.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我突然覺得我對阿人一無所知
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.88,0:18:35.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是可以確定的是他是一個好人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.40,0:18:38.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相信他吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.28,0:19:03.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？怎麼關掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.81,0:19:08.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀 大家過得愉快嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.50,0:19:10.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人類的諸位..
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.15,0:19:15.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想告訴大家一件有趣的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.41,0:19:19.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以強制性的讓所有人把注意放在我身上
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.88,0:19:21.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊 沒前沒後的..
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.20,0:19:26.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先來個自我介紹吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.86,0:19:28.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們是艾波爾
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.86,0:19:28.22,Zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(715,660)}EVOL
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.20,0:19:30.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別看我這樣 我可不是人類
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.43,0:19:32.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,灰谷..
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.28,0:19:37.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾波爾是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.36,0:19:40.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,百聞不如一見
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.78,0:19:43.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會把攝像機切換到外景
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.89,0:19:46.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位先看一看這個吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.73,0:19:48.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了各位
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.40,0:19:50.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,let's“里返”
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.58,0:19:53.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 這是哪門子惡作劇啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.35,0:19:55.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,腦子有問題吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.59,0:19:58.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有問題的是誰啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.09,0:20:09.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這什麼啊 每個頻道都一樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.32,0:20:10.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請關掉它！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.37,0:20:16.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呢 感覺有點惡心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.89,0:20:23.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.12,0:20:25.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿姨 是我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.15,0:20:26.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳有在看電視嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.61,0:20:29.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看了啊 在播很奇怪的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.56,0:20:31.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我馬上就關掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.93,0:20:32.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.65,0:20:35.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有 小葉在妳那裡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.64,0:20:38.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她不在哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.76,0:20:39.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話就算了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.24,0:20:42.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是如果小葉去妳那裡的話
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.60,0:20:43.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請讓她進屋子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.90,0:20:45.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對不要讓小葉到外面去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.65,0:20:47.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？怎麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.82,0:20:49.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之拜託妳了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.67,0:20:57.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另一個人去了中城
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.32,0:21:01.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是高雅的話會優先選擇妹妹吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.74,0:21:04.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是結果就是這個
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.12,0:21:10.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位是否看得很盡興？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.24,0:21:13.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實我們是人類創造出來的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.59,0:21:17.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了把我們的自相殘殺當成娛樂節目來賣錢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.78,0:21:20.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是有一天我們察覺到了..
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.14,0:21:24.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼我們要這麼做不可？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.13,0:21:27.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於是我們很火大
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.87,0:21:29.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 我們決定了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.06,0:21:34.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們要向人類發起復仇
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.75,0:21:45.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這下你無法救到所有人了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.56,0:21:51.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的正義有個重大的缺陷
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.36,0:21:53.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底缺了什麼呢..
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.18,0:22:00.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.25,0:22:14.34,ED_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}誕生日が来るとね
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.25,0:22:14.34,ED_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}每一次生日來臨的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.26,0:22:21.80,ED_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}選ぶ　あなたへのプレゼント
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.26,0:22:21.80,ED_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}挑選 給你的禮物
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.07,0:22:29.06,ED_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}五番街通り 足をとめたって
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.07,0:22:29.06,ED_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}哪怕駐足於第五大道
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.43,0:22:34.86,ED_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}この愛代えられない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.43,0:22:34.86,ED_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}也無法買到我對你的這份愛
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.68,0:22:45.13,ED_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Darling　時計を止めて　頭を止めて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.68,0:22:45.13,ED_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}親愛的 停下時鐘 停止思考
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.63,0:22:51.08,ED_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}心を止める　目も、耳もぜんぶ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.63,0:22:51.08,ED_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}停止心跳 眼睛..耳朵..停止你的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.32,0:22:57.76,ED_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Darling　あなたにもらった言葉のすべて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.32,0:22:57.76,ED_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}親愛的 你給予我的每一句話語
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.34,0:23:03.88,ED_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}刺の無い薔薇を抱きしめたように
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.34,0:23:03.88,ED_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}我都會當做無棘的玫瑰緊緊抱在懷裏
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.33,0:23:08.65,ED_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}hugging' you
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.33,0:23:08.65,ED_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}擁抱你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.74,0:23:16.93,ED_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Darling　この世界でふたり出会った奇跡
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.74,0:23:16.93,ED_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}親愛的 兩人在這個世界邂逅的奇跡
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.34,0:23:22.85,ED_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}その跡をつけてばかりの私、
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.34,0:23:22.85,ED_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}只能悄悄跟在你後面的我
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.29,0:23:28.26,ED_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}lovin' you
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.29,0:23:28.26,ED_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}深愛著你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.10,0:23:35.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.60,0:23:37.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好不可思議..
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.29,0:23:39.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明身處這種狀況..
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.38,0:23:41.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明這麼痛苦..
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.43,0:23:45.42,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(1022,530)}{\fad(550,0)}操控人偶
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.49,0:23:44.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是..這份熱血沸騰的感覺！
